{"id":86,"parent_id":73,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":86,"title":"John 13","subtitle":"","short_title":"John","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 13"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus washes the feet of the Twelve—He identifies Judas as His betrayer—He commands them to love one another."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.1","order":"03.06.013.10829"},["b","1"],"Now before the feast of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"passover"],", when Jesus knew that his hour was come that he should depart out of this world unto the Father, having loved his own which were in the world, he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"loved"],"them unto the end."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.2","order":"03.06.013.10830"},["b","2"],"And supper being ended, the devil having now put into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"heart"],"of Judas Iscariot, Simon’s",["i","son,"],"to betray him;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.3","order":"03.06.013.10831"},["b","3"],"Jesus",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"knowing"],"that the Father had given all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"things"],"into his hands, and that he was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"come"],"from God, and went to God;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.4","order":"03.06.013.10832"},["b","4"],"He riseth from supper, and laid aside his garments; and took a towel, and girded himself."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.5","order":"03.06.013.10833"},["b","5"],"After that he poureth water into a basin, and began to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"wash"],"the disciples’ feet, and to wipe",["i","them"],"with the towel wherewith he was girded."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.6","order":"03.06.013.10834"},["b","6"],"Then cometh he to Simon Peter: and Peter saith unto him, Lord, dost thou wash my feet?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.7","order":"03.06.013.10835"},["b","7"],"Jesus answered and said unto him, What I do thou knowest not now; but thou shalt know hereafter."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.8","order":"03.06.013.10836"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Peter"],"saith unto him, Thou shalt never wash my feet. Jesus answered him, If I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"wash"],"thee not, thou hast no part with me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.9","order":"03.06.013.10837"},["b","9"],"Simon Peter saith unto him, Lord, not my feet only, but also",["i","my"],"hands and",["i","my"],"head."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.10","order":"03.06.013.10838"},["b","10"],"Jesus saith to him, He that is washed needeth not save to wash",["i","his"],"feet, but is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"clean"],"every whit: and ye are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"clean"],", but not all."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.11","order":"03.06.013.10839"},["b","11"],"For he knew who should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"betray"],"him; therefore said he, Ye are not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"all"],"clean."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.12","order":"03.06.013.10840"},["b","12"],"So after he had washed their feet, and had taken his garments, and was set down again, he said unto them, Know ye what I have done to you?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.13","order":"03.06.013.10841"},["b","13"],"Ye call me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Master"],"and Lord: and ye say well; for",["i","so"],"I am."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.14","order":"03.06.013.10842"},["b","14"],"If I then,",["i","your"],"Lord and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Master"],", have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"washed"],"your feet; ye also ought to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"wash"],"one another’s",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"feet"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.15","order":"03.06.013.10843"},["b","15"],"For I have given you an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"example"],", that ye should do as I have done to you."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.16","order":"03.06.013.10844"},["b","16"],"Verily, verily, I say unto you, The servant is not greater than his lord; neither he that is sent greater than he that sent him."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.17","order":"03.06.013.10845"},["b","17"],"If ye know these things,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"happy"],"are ye if ye do them."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.18","order":"03.06.013.10846"},["b","18"],"¶I speak not of you all: I know whom I have chosen: but that the scripture may be fulfilled, He that eateth bread with me hath lifted up his heel against me."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.19","order":"03.06.013.10847"},["b","19"],"Now I tell you before it come, that, when it is come to pass, ye may believe that I am",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"he"],"."]],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.20","order":"03.06.013.10848"},["b","20"],"Verily, verily, I say unto you, He that receiveth whomsoever I send",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"receiveth"],"me; and he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"receiveth"],"me receiveth him that sent me."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.21","order":"03.06.013.10849"},["b","21"],"When Jesus had thus said, he was troubled in spirit, and testified, and said, Verily, verily, I say unto you, that one of you shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"betray"],"me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.22","order":"03.06.013.10850"},["b","22"],"Then the disciples looked one on another, doubting of whom he spake."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.23","order":"03.06.013.10851"},["b","23"],"Now there was leaning on Jesus’ bosom one of his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"disciples"],", whom Jesus loved."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.24","order":"03.06.013.10852"},["b","24"],"Simon Peter therefore beckoned to him, that he should ask who it should be of whom he spake."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.25","order":"03.06.013.10853"},["b","25"],"He then lying on Jesus’ breast saith unto him, Lord, who is it?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.26","order":"03.06.013.10854"},["b","26"],"Jesus answered, He it is, to whom I shall give a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"sop"],", when I have dipped",["i","it."],"And when he had dipped the sop, he gave",["i","it"],"to Judas Iscariot,",["i","the son"],"of Simon."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.27","order":"03.06.013.10855"},["b","27"],"And after the sop",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"Satan"],"entered into him. Then said Jesus unto him, That thou doest, do quickly."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.28","order":"03.06.013.10856"},["b","28"],"Now no man at the table knew for what intent he spake this unto him."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.29","order":"03.06.013.10857"},["b","29"],"For some",["i","of them"],"thought, because Judas had the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"bag"],", that Jesus had said unto him, Buy",["i","those things"],"that we have need of against the feast; or, that he should give something to the poor."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.30","order":"03.06.013.10858"},["b","30"],"He then having received the sop went immediately out: and it was night."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.31","order":"03.06.013.10859"},["b","31"],"¶Therefore, when he was gone out, Jesus said, Now is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"Son of man"],"glorified, and God is glorified in him."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.32","order":"03.06.013.10860"},["b","32"],"If God be glorified in him, God shall also glorify him in himself, and shall straightway glorify him."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.33","order":"03.06.013.10861"},["b","33"],"Little children, yet a little while I am with you. Ye shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"seek"],"me: and as I said unto the Jews, Whither I go, ye cannot come; so now I say to you."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.34","order":"03.06.013.10862"},["b","34"],"A new commandment I give unto you, That ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"love"],"one another; as I have loved you, that ye also",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"love"],"one another."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.35","order":"03.06.013.10863"},["b","35"],"By this shall all",["i","men"],"know that ye are my disciples, if ye have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"love"],"one to another."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.36","order":"03.06.013.10864"},["b","36"],"¶Simon Peter said unto him, Lord, whither goest thou? Jesus answered him, Whither I go, thou canst not follow me now; but thou shalt follow me afterwards."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.37","order":"03.06.013.10865"},["b","37"],"Peter said unto him, Lord, why cannot I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"follow"],"thee now? I will lay down my life for thy sake."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.38","order":"03.06.013.10866"},["b","38"],"Jesus answered him, Wilt thou lay down thy life for my sake? Verily, verily, I say unto thee, The cock shall not crow, till thou hast denied me thrice."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.1a","order":"03.06.013.10867"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/16.1"},"Deut. 16:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.1b","order":"03.06.013.10869"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"TG God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.2a","order":"03.06.013.10871"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.15.13,15"},"D&C 10:15 (13, 15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.28"},"63:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.3a","order":"03.06.013.10873"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.3b","order":"03.06.013.10875"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.3c","order":"03.06.013.10877"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.29"},"John 7:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.5a","order":"03.06.013.10879"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wash"},"TG Wash"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.8a","order":"03.06.013.10881"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-john/13.8-10"},["span.small","JST"],"John 13:8–10 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.8b","order":"03.06.013.10883"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purification"},"TG Purification"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.10a","order":"03.06.013.10885"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"TG Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.10b","order":"03.06.013.10887"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.10"},"D&C 38:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.11a","order":"03.06.013.10889"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/6.64"},"John 6:64"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.11b","order":"03.06.013.10891"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.3"},"D&C 66:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.13a","order":"03.06.013.10893"},["b","13a"],["span.small","GR"],"Teacher."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.14a","order":"03.06.013.10895"},["b","14a"],["span.small","GR"],"Teacher."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.14b","order":"03.06.013.10897"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courtesy"},"TG Courtesy"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.14c","order":"03.06.013.10899"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/humility"},"TG Humility"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.14d","order":"03.06.013.10901"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-teaching-mode-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Teaching Mode of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.15a","order":"03.06.013.10903"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/example"},"TG Example"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-the-standard-of-righteousness"},"God, the Standard of Righteousness"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.17a","order":"03.06.013.10905"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.19a","order":"03.06.013.10907"},["b","19a"],["span.small","JST"],"John 13:19 …",["i","the Christ."]],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.20a","order":"03.06.013.10909"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.5"},"D&C 39:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.37"},"84:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.20b","order":"03.06.013.10911"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/4.6.1-6"},"1 Jn. 4:6 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.21a","order":"03.06.013.10913"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-betrayal-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Betrayal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.23a","order":"03.06.013.10915"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/20.2"},"John 20:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/21.24.20-24"},"21:24 (20–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.26a","order":"03.06.013.10917"},["b","26a"],["span.small","GR"],"morsel, mouthful."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.27a","order":"03.06.013.10919"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.29a","order":"03.06.013.10921"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.6"},"John 12:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.31a","order":"03.06.013.10923"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-son-of-man"},"TG Jesus Christ, Son of Man"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.33a","order":"03.06.013.10925"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.34.33-36"},"John 7:34 (33–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.34a","order":"03.06.013.10927"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"TG Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.34b","order":"03.06.013.10929"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.35a","order":"03.06.013.10931"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fellowshipping"},"TG Fellowshipping"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-love-of"},"God, Love of"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.37a","order":"03.06.013.10933"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."]]}
